            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="meta-taskdescription" metaValue="Add or modify the components and its quantities. Along with this, maintain the details like co-product, alternate item group, etc. &#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;Categorization of the items in a BOM according to set criteria, such as whether they refer to an object (for example, material master or document info record) or whether they are kept in stock. &#10;&#10;Item Category: Description &#10;C: Compatible Unit&#10;D: Document item&#10;I: PM structure element&#10;K: Class item&#10;L: Stock item&#10;M: Intra material&#10;N: Non-stock item&#10;R: Variable-size item&#10;T: Text item"/>
